name: Reflections In Moonlight
description:
I took advantage
of seeing the moon,
in all of its beauty.
The gorgeous, mesmerizing
reflections in the ocean.
I knew I would be in bliss
when I would actually behold it
with sand between toes
crisp ocean air, a slight breeze,
I was no longer trapped.
It felt so real 
I could taste it.
in person.
